vivado.report\_level
Vivado optimization level, sets other vivado\_\* options. This will not apply to IP/XO output. The choices are 0, 1, 2, 3. This only applies for report generation and will not apply to the exported IP. The default setting is 0. Specify a Pblock range to use during implementation for reporting purposes.
vivado.pblock={SLICE_X8Y105:SLICE_X23Y149}

