Nets
The Nets table shows details of the net connections made between the AI Engine kernels, or the AI Engine kernel and the PLIO/GMIO ports. For example, the code snippet below from the graph.h file provides examples of the connect constraint used to connect to the stream and window connections between the AI Engine ker...
connect(in.out[0], interpolator.in[0]);
connect(interpolator.out[0], clip_in.[0]);
connect(clip_out.out[0], classify.in[0]);
connect(classify.out[0], out.in[0]);
